oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Photograph of a portion of a National Guard unit from Etowah, Tennessee
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Photograph of a portion of the Etowah (Tenn.) National Guard at the 9th St. Armory. They are part of Co. L, 117th Inf., 30th Div. and their names are listed on the reverse. There are two girls and a young boy with the group. The group includes Riley Murphy who was killed in France.
